{"tid":2137900,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"17歲男生涉「黎明行動」垃圾桶堵路 獲撤控簽保守行為結案","createTime":"2020-08-03T09:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T09:45:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a3f048802b5e846532e89633997cc7ceeffbad","tid":2137900,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:14:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F7701&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F732HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=96a26377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7701</a><br />\n<br />\n#觀塘裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#徐綺薇主任裁判官 <br />\n#提堂 #1111九龍灣<br />\n<br />\n楊 (17)<br />\n<br />\n控罪 ： 公眾地方造成阻礙<br />\n第228章《簡易程序治罪條例》第4a條<br />\n被控於2019年11月11日，在九龍灣站外馬路，無合理辯解及解釋投放一個垃圾桶於馬路中，對馬路使用者做成一定阻礙及不便。<br />\n<br />\n以$2000簽保守行為12個月<br />\n堂費$1000，證物3-9歸還被告"},{"pid":"2d531c8431f6d928768b159700f47797f8288c93","tid":2137900,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839d76b6a273e59fa8ba8d254a9c49c2bf5e95f7","tid":2137900,"uid":80851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:16:28.000Z","msg":"另一個官竟然唔俾保釋要還押<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d41db974523d9ea745eb893294ed9fed6aa912","tid":2137900,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d531c8431f6d928768b159700f47797f8288c93","tid":2137900,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T09:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><